<p>I have a list that looks something like this:</p>  <pre><code>&lt;ul id='mylist'&gt;     &lt;li&gt;         &lt;input val="1"&gt;     &lt;/li&gt;     &lt;li&gt;         &lt;input val="2"&gt;     &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; </code></pre>  <p>How can I use JQuery to select an input by value? I can get a list of li's by doing</p>  <pre><code>$("#mylist").children('li') </code></pre>  <p>but can't work out how to then get the inputs.</p>